        <Document ID="44335A45-771D-426C-BD5A-73AE4C140084">
            <Title>Page 22: 2010</Title>
            <Text>PAGE &lt;$N&gt;

PANEL 1

INTERIOR: 1988. DAY. SAULS HOUSE. THE HALL. Saul coming down the stairs, unkempt - hair all over the place, wearing nothing but socks and underpants.

PANEL 2

He picks up letters from the floor.

PANEL 3

INTERIOR: 1988. DAY. SAULS HOUSE. THE KITCHEN. Saul standing in the kitchen looking at a fairly thick set of papers.

PANEL 4

Over his shoulder, we can see they are divorce papers.

PANEL 5

INTERIOR: 1988. DAY. SAULS HOUSE. THE HALL. SAUL is walking up the stairs.

SAUL
I need a drink.

PANEL 6

Saul is walking up his garden path, moving away from his house. He is putting his left arm into the sleeve of his jacket as he walks.

SAUL (CONT'D)
Bitch.


</Text>
