EXTERIOR: 1762. NIGHT. RIVER DOCKS   VALLADOLID. FRANCISCO, aged 16, and a girl his own age, lay in the bottom of a row boat. The boat is tied to a series of other boats and the end boat is tied to the deserted quay. They are naked and entwined. They have obviously just had sex. They are covered in sweat and their hair is disarranged. They are very happy and content.

