ALODIA, FRANCISCO, MARTA and GABRIEL are all standing in the hall. ALODIA is incandescent. FRANCISCO is smothering his laughter. GABRIEL is torn between the two, but stands behind ALODIA because he is trying to hide his indulgence of the boy.

