EXTERIOR: 2013. NIGHT.  THE RIVER BANK. DEEP IN THE FOREST. SAUL and ISABEL are standing by the side of the river. In the background we see the FERRY WOMAN standing by her boat. ISABEL is pointing towards the FERRY WOMAN.

ISABEL
Stop ringing the bell, idiota. She's right there.

