PANEL 1

INTERIOR: 2013. DAY. FERRY WOMANS HOUSE. RIVER BANK. DEEP IN THE FOREST. SAUL lays in the bed. ISABEL sits in an armchair by his side. The FERRY WOMAN is pottering around in the room doing something.

